//
//It checks to see if you have something equipped in your left
//hand (like a 2-handed weapon) and if you do, it un-equips
//it, uses a potion (cure in this example), then requips. else
//if you don't have anything in your left hand then it just
//uses the potion.
//
if @findlayer 'self' 2
  togglehands 'left'
  pause 600
  usetype! 0xf07
  pause 600
  togglehands 'left'
else
  usetype! 0xf07
endif
